column5: CTV was just talking about the lady X country skier that crashed off the embankment during practice. She went on to win the bronze in her 10K race the next day. With 4 broken ribs and a punctured lung!!!!! That takes grit and determination!!!!!!
Can't be true... cherry says Europeans are soft  Gusty performance!
holy crap....that doesnt say much for the people that lost to her...wonder how she is going to pass the drug test
I saw that too.. thats one tough girl.   broken ribs and a collapsed lung, they fix her up and she get the bronze..
Ya, I saw that!  She even had to be assisted onto the podium to accept her medal!  Wow!!!
She and Rochette win the first Terry Fox award for courage.  http://www.vancouversun.com/Rochette+Majdi...4650/story.html
